{"tid":881117,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(放假先俾你有優惠) 港鐵下月3日及4日推優惠 成人八達通享特惠票價","createTime":"2018-10-29T07:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T09:04:34.000Z","uid":58275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dee7c078d8086d453a76725929200adcc416f928","tid":881117,"uid":58275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"鐵路事宜小組委員會召開會議討論港鐵早前四條鐵路綫路服務受阻事故。港鐵車務總監劉天成表示，港鐵將於即將的周末推出一次性優惠，即十一月三日及四日，使用成人八達通的乘客在這兩天票價，將享用特惠車票的票價，本來享用特惠票價的人士則每次車程票價為一元。劉天成當時沒有提及有否行程次數上限及路綫限制。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長陳帆指，政府及港鐵十分關注事件，全力調查當日事故的原因，政府已要求全力調查，並在兩個月內提交報告，又說他在上周三立法會會議已承諾檢討現行應變措施，包括接駁巴士問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壞就番工個日, 補獲就放假先俾你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%8A4%E6%97%A5%E6%8E%A8%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E3%80%80%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%AB%E7%89%B9%E6%83%A0%E7%A5%A8%E5%83%B9-070352955.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%25883%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%258A4%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2584%25AA%25E6%2583%25A0%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E5%2583%25B9-070352955.html&d=7329xsprZlMi8AYOta0tnBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=2c48a3f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%8A4%E6%97%A5%E6%8E%A8%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E3%80%80%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%AB%E7%89%B9%E6%83%A0%E7%A5%A8%E5%83%B9-070352955.html</a>"},{"pid":"622f207b40bc84cf477bdcea0406d88af2376e92","tid":881117,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1